Well I first inteanded this map to be a simple headshot practice map for a friend that had requested it over skype, but I found myself developing the map more and more into a more visually appealing and more fun map to play. So yer, download it, play it for a short while get bored, give some feedback and just genrally waste some time that you could have spent eating some rather tasty chocolate digestives :P. ~Enjoy! Feedback would also be great!

Fav this map! Watch me as a submitter :)
